- Dispatch lives in `internal/node/attach.go` `func (a *attacher) handle(ctx, msg)` — a `switch m := msg.Msg.(type)` over `*nodev1.CPMessage_Start`, `_Stop`, `_Open`, `_Close`, `_Frame`, `_CreateSession`, `_CloseSession`, default.
