- Spawn lookup: `a.mgr.Store().Get(spawnID) (*spawnlet.Spawn, bool)`. `spawnlet.Spawn` has `ControlToken string`, `ControlURL string` ("http://<PodIP>:<controlPort>/control/model", empty if pod has no IP), and `Generation uint64`. `Manager.Store()` returns the `*Store`.
