- **Spec coverage:** Implements the spec §Testing "End-to-end" bullet verbatim — "start spawn → SetSpawnModel → assert the next request leaving the sidecar carries the new model id," realized as the faithful sidecar-level proof (start sidecar → set override via control endpoint → next forwarded request carries the new id). Justification for not using full CP path SetSpawnModel for the *capture* is documented above (uncapturable upstream + no `SIDECAR_UPSTREAM` override in the manager).
